    GetPrimitiveRestartValue
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetPrimitiveRestartValue</TypeRef> method returns the index value used to represent a primitive restart for the instantiated type.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[static T GetPrimitiveRestartValue();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="static T">
        The primitive restart value for this index attribute data type.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
